values: 一束；一捆；一串；束；捆；串；一群；一大批；扎；大量；许多；（扎在头两侧的）辫子
捆扎；集中；聚集；挤作一团；组成一群；紧束；使成束

pos_mean_info_list.mean: 形成一串；隆起；集中（bunch的过去分词）

word_mean_info__list.difference: 着重指邮包，也指将东西扎成小包或不太大的包。
指包装整齐严密的包裹或一包、一捆、一盒东西。
指多件东西被捆扎在一起。
指有规则地把同类东西固定在一起。
一般指小件行李、邮包、还可指更小一些的包。
指专为背负而包扎的包裹，也指驮物等。

word_group.brief_definition: 挤在一起；聚成一团；捆在一起
一群(或堆)坏的里较好者, 矮子中的将军
word_group.phrase: the best of a bad bunch

bilingual.source: She tied the balloons into a bunch.
I bought a bunch of flowers for my mom.
bilingual.target: 我买了一束花送给妈妈。

bilingual.source: He is holding a bunch of keys in his hand.
I bought a bunch of flowers at the market.
bilingual.target: 我在市场上买了一束花。

bilingual.source: She placed a bunch of floret on the table.
bilingual.target: 她在桌子上摆了一束小花。

bilingual.source: This a bunch of flowers smells very fragrant.
bilingual.target: 这一束花闻起来非常香。

bilingual.source: She bought a bunch of flowers for her mother.
bilingual.target: 她给她妈妈买了一束花。

bilingual.source: The children gathered a bunch of wildflowers.
bilingual.target: 孩子们采集了一束野花。

bilingual.source: We bought a bunch of bananas at the market.
bilingual.target: 我们在市场上买了一束香蕉。

list.abstract: bunch，英语单词，名词、动词，作名词时译为“群；串；突出物”，作动词时译为“隆起；打褶；形成一串；使成一串；使打褶”。

yingyinNormal.en: What a bunch of crybabies. No guts, no glory, man.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真是一群爱哭鬼，人有多大胆，地有多大产。

yingyinNormal.en: You're flapping around like a bunch of drunken ducks!
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们就像一群喝醉的鸭子，四处乱飞。

yingyinNormal.en: Singapore's animal residents are a pretty diverse bunch too!
yingyinNormal.zh: 新加坡有各种各样的动物，小心为上。

yingyinNormal.en: Wait! She said that you crammed a bunch of rocks in it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等等，她说你在里面塞了很多石子。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you with a girl? No, no. It's a bunch of cheerleaders.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你和别的女人在一起? 不不 是...是一群啦啦队员。

yingyinNormal.en: Droning on to a bunch of hung over English majors? Exactly.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对一群宿醉未消的英语专业大学生唠叨吗？没错。

yingyinNormal.en: I am not gonna let a bunch of itchy spots stand between us.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不会让这里也痒，那里也痒分开我们两个。

yingyinNormal.en: Isn't it a shame when one girl ruins it for the whole bunch?
yingyinNormal.zh: 真是糟糕，一个女孩就毁了大家。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, what were you gonna do with a bunch of sharpened rocks?
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，那你需要削过的石头来做什么呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Look. Ugly Naked Guy lit a bunch of candles. That had to hurt.
yingyinNormal.zh: 瞧，丑陋裸男点燃了几根蜡烛。一定很痛。

yingyinNormal.en: I'd move into a huge mansion, buy a bunch of cool shit, not be poor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要住进大豪宅，买一堆超酷的玩意儿，再也不当穷人。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm sorry. I didn't know how this machine worked. What a bunch of a-holes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对不起，我不知道这个机器怎么这样。一群废物。

yingyinNormal.en: I want you to throw him off his game. Start by asking a bunch of questions.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我要你混淆视听，打乱他的节奏，首先问他一堆问题。

yingyinNormal.en: A desperate bunch of mercenaries, if ever there was, Sire. Hold your tongue!
yingyinNormal.zh: 看样子是群下贱的佣兵，大人。住嘴。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, guys. More Halloween candy? Didn't you just buy a bunch of it yesterday?
yingyinNormal.zh: 伙计们。又买万圣节糖果了啊？你昨天不是刚买了一堆吗？

yingyinNormal.en: He's bringing me; who are you bringing? Wow, what a bunch of Nosey O'Donnells.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他带我来啊，你带谁呢？哎哟，好一群多管闲事的美国佬啊。

yingyinNormal.en: It'll just be a bunch of my friends. We'll have some beer, do a little dancing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 其实也就是邀请一帮朋友，喝喝啤酒，跳跳舞。

yingyinNormal.en: No, I've applied a bunch of schools, Fordham let me in. Why do you go to Shaffer?
yingyinNormal.zh: 也不是，我申请了一堆学校，福特汉姆录了我，那你为什么去谢尔佛？

yingyinNormal.en: Marsha, Jan and Cindy were the three daughters in what TV family? The Brady bunch.
yingyinNormal.zh: 玛莎，简，和辛迪是哪部电视剧中的三姐妹？是"脱线家族"。

yingyinNormal.en: I know. Why don't she get drunk. That worked for a bunch of girls in my high school.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那她喝个烂醉如何？我很多高中同学都是这样搞大肚子的。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: They're part of a <highlight>bunch</highlight> of celebrities starring in a new video for World Environment Day.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他们是出演世界环境日新视频的那群名人中的一员。
